{"tid":773680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁家榮：我為亞視誤報江澤民死訊承擔最大責任","createTime":"2018-08-09T17:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T17:50:44.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9fe25587aaca344e7319d4772425a66c2c68eb6","tid":773680,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"新任廣播處處長梁家榮履新，他表示，自己是新丁，未來一定會與同事商討港台發展方向，港台會繼續維持編輯自主。<br />\n<br />\n梁家榮表示，對於亞視誤報江澤民死訊事件，自己是當時新聞部最高負責人，承擔最大責任。當晚，他已打了辭職信，其後亦在不同場合作詳細交代，而通訊管理局已有判決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/117570-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%AA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E6%AD%BB%E8%A8%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6+%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E6%A6%AE%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F117570-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%2B%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB&d=um9KhaGFcCcSmGPdFj9BVttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=73d60252\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F117570-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%2B%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB&h=66f882ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/117570-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%AA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E6%AD%BB%E8%A8%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6+%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E6%A6%AE%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB</a>"},{"pid":"c070ab2d2d2cf94fa43e8dd36b820a43d7b10fd8","tid":773680,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img sr